column5: Managed to get out for a morning fish on kbay.  I didn't crush it today but managed to hook a few nice fish.  Biggest of the morning was 5.31 pounds.  Nice fish and of course was very fat.
very healthy looking fish, very nice
Sounds like a fun time. Nice fish!
I'd have a fat smile too with a smallie like that one.
Now thats what im talking about! Very nice fish, no matter how cold it is, that fish puts a smile on anyones face!
Nice fish Chris. Handful of boats out there this morning. Wheres the Mow?
Nice fish for sure.  It only take him minutes of thinking of the style he want's for it to grow in and it's there.
Moustachio is on its way.  By next week I hope to post pics with a definate cookie duster in place
Nice chunk of bronze Chris    Congrats
Nice Chris!  See you out there soon. Glad to see you're out doing something you love.
